movies.title: A Hidden Life
movies.description: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins due to the efforts of the Mad Titan, Thanos. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers must assemble once more in order to undo Thanos’ actions and restore order to the universe once and for all, no matter what consequences may be in store.

series.title: Stranger Things
series.description: When a young boy vanishes, a small town uncovers a mystery involving secret experiments, terrifying supernatural forces and one strange little girl. Watch all you want. This nostalgic nod to '80s sci-fi and horror classics has earned dozens of Emmy nominations, including three for Outstanding Drama.
